column5: Any one fish this fairly remote water. I have MANY times...........................
Len - i just dropped you a PM. phish

I might be making a trip up that way again this year, it's been quite a few years. I'll be at Pash in June but a friend wants to revisit Windigo or maybe one of the other lakes up there. Are you heading to Horseshoe this year?
Thank you phish--YOU are the guy I WANT TO BE WHEN I grow up. Just turned 78 this month.
Just turned a young 78---Doubt I will be back. Thinking of a couple remote lakes north of Terrace Bay......
